  AFFECTS: users of multimedia/ffmpeg1 and multimedia/ffmpeg-devel
  AUTHOR: wg@FreeBSD.org

  The port ffmpeg was updated, ffmpeg1 and ffmpeg-devel were removed in
  favor of ffmpeg.

